title: Call of Duty Returns To World War 2? - Kinda Funny Games Daily 03.26.21
description:
Spawn On Me's Kahlief Adams joins us to talk about Call of Duty: WWIII Vanguard, BAFTA Awards, and more!

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:05:23 - Housekeeping
It’s a big day for Kinda Funny Reactions! Today over on Youtube.com/KindaFunny you can catch:
Falcon and The Winter Soldier episode 2 reactions
Invincible reactions
And then The Suicide Squad trailer reactions
Next Wednesday, after KFGD: Greg’s stream is raising money for the American Heart Association! Tune in for the normal Wednesday stream but this time for a good cause!
The Roper Report   -
00:06:23 - ID @ Xbox
00:10:00 - This year's Call of Duty returns to WW2
00:22:08 - Hades wins Best Game at BAFTA Games Awards 2021
00:26:25 - That Microsoft Discord acquisition could happen as soon as next month
00:30:43 -  Ad 
00:35:38 - Outriders Will Permanently Brand Cheaters
00:38:16 - PSA: Balan Wonderworld’s Day one patch is set to fix epileptic triggers in the game
00:42:35 - Out today 
00:44:24 - “Is there more pressure than ever on these upcoming video game movies to actually hit?” - Jordan Rowan
00:52:09 - It’s KFGD’s 900th episode!
01:00:45 - You‘re Wrong
01:05:31 - Post Show
Next Week’s Hosts:
MON: Blessing and Greg
TUES: Greg and Gary Whitta
WED: Blessing and Tim
THUR: Andy & Nick (for the highly anticipated April Fool’s episode)
FRI: Blessing and Lucy James from Gamespot
